Description
Totems that slept for many years are now awaken!!! Take your guns and stop the ancient evil! Chose a revolver, a shotgun or an ak-48 as your instrument of destruction and start the TEMPLE FIGHT!!! 

FEATURES: 
- Different guns for different battle tactics 
- Fun and addicting gameplay 
- Cool sounds 
- Gradually increasing level of difficulty
